  "short_description": "Intergalacto-1 offers a unique experience with three distinct modes. Engage in PvP battles in Warzone mode, survive mystical horrors in Mystic Town: THE ABYSS, and explore hidden worlds while battling zombies and confronting the boss, INM. Enjoy diverse challenges and rich gameplay.",
